race.description: Sky International Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: KID BILLY (3) comes here in peak condition and brings the right figures to take this out. Launched late in the small field when second over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Gets weight relief today and should appreciate the 1400m. REPEAT OFFENDER (10) lightly raced filly who returned good closing splits at her second race start with a solid fourth over 1250m at this track. Hard to beat in this suitable race. ARGERICH (4) snagged back from the wide gate and savaged the line late when fourth over 1500m at Port Macquarie. On the quick backup and expected to go close. FINDING ELLE (8) finds a weaker contest and can take a hand in the finish after running fourth over 1300m at Ballina.
